# Flash sector wear levelling: pick least-worn sector.
*pick(wears as Vec of i64, n as i64) returns i64
    best is 0
    bw is wears.get(0)
    i is 1
    while i < n
        if wears.get(i) < bw
            bw is wears.get(i)
            best is i
        i is i + 1
    best

*main
    w is vec()
    w.push(120)
    w.push(50)
    w.push(80)
    w.push(15)
    w.push(200)
    log pick(w, 5)
